quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,55,"inn ke maal o doulat aur un ki kasrat aulaad ko dekh kar dhoka nah khao, Allah to yeh chahta hai ke aِnhi cheezon ke zareya se un ko duniya ki zindagi mein bhi mbtlaye azaab kere aur yeh jaan bhi den to inkaar haq hi ki haalat mein den"
9,56,"woh khuda ki qasam kha kha kar kehte hain ke hum tumhi mein se hain, halaank woh hargiz tum mein se nahi hain asal mein to woh aisay log hain jo tum se khauf zada hain"
9,57,"agar woh koi jaye panah paleen ya koi khoh ya ghis bethnay ki jagah, to bhaag kar uss mein ja chhpin"
9,58,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un mein se baaz log sadqat ki taqseem mein tum par aitrazaat karte hain agar is maal mein se inhen kuch day diya jaye to khoo sh ho jayen, aur nah diya jaye to bighrnay lagtay hain"
9,59,"kya acha hota ke Allah aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne jo kuch bhi inhen diya tha is par woh raazi rehtay aur kehte ke"" Allah hamaray liye kaafi hai, woh apne fazl se hamein bohat kuch day ga aur is ka rasool bhi hum par inayat farmaiye ga, hum Allah hi ki taraf nazar jamaye hue hain """
9,60,"yeh sadqat to darasal faqeero aur miskeeno ke liye hain aur unn logon ke liye jo sadqat ke kaam par mamoor hon, aur unn ke liye jin ki taleef qalb matloob ho neez yeh gardnon ke chhuranay aur qarz daaron ki madad karne mein aur raah khuda mein aur musafir nawazi mein istemaal karne ke liye hain aik fareeza hai Allah ki taraf se aur Allah sab kuch jan-nay wala aur Dana o Beena hai"
9,61,"un mein se kuch log hain jo apni baton se nabi ko dukh dete hain aur kehte hain ke yeh shakhs kaanon ka kacha hai kaho,"" woh tumhari bhalai ke liye aisa hai, Allah par imaan rakhta hai aur ahal imaan par aetmaad karta hai aur sara sar rehmat hai un logon ke liye jo tum mein se imandaar hain aur jo log Allah ke rasool ko dukh dete hain un ke liye dard naak saza hai """
